Class BrosDate

  • java.lang.Object
    • BrosDate

  • public class BrosDate
extends java.lang.Object
    The BrosDate class contains utility methods to facilitate the handling of Date objects.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      BrosDate()
      Constructs a BrosDate object which represents the current date and time.

        strDateTime - date and time represented in the format "dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm" (24 hr format). E.g. "09/12/2000 16:00" represents 4pm on Dec 9, 2000.
